<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Shadowban Explained</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Syne:wght@800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: #0a0a0f;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
min-height: 100vh;
font-family: ‘Space Grotesk’, sans-serif;
overflow: hidden;
}

.card {
width: 480px;
background: #0f0f1a;
border-radius: 28px;
padding: 36px 32px;
position: relative;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
overflow: hidden;
}

/* Glow blobs */
.blob1 {
position: absolute;
width: 300px; height: 300px;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(120,60,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
top: -80px; right: -80px;
border-radius: 50%;
pointer-events: none;
}
.blob2 {
position: absolute;
width: 200px; height: 200px;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,60,120,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
bottom: -40px; left: -40px;
border-radius: 50%;
pointer-events: none;
}

/* Header */
.badge {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 6px;
background: rgba(120,60,255,0.15);
border: 1px solid rgba(120,60,255,0.35);
border-radius: 100px;
padding: 5px 14px;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #a084ff;
letter-spacing: 0.08em;
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.badge .dot {
width: 7px; height: 7px;
background: #a084ff;
border-radius: 50%;
animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse {
0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.7); }
}

.title {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: 38px;
font-weight: 900;
line-height: 1.05;
color: #fff;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.title .ghost {
color: transparent;
-webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
}
.title .highlight {
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a084ff, #ff6eb4);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
background-clip: text;
}

.subtitle {
font-size: 13.5px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
margin-bottom: 26px;
line-height: 1.5;
}

/* What is it section */
.what-box {
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 18px 20px;
margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.what-box .label {
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.12em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.what-box p {
font-size: 13.5px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
line-height: 1.6;
}
.what-box p span {
color: #ff6eb4;
font-weight: 700;
}

/* Triggers */
.section-title {
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.12em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.triggers {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 9px;
margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.trigger-row {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 12px;
background: rgba(255,80,100,0.07);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,80,100,0.15);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 11px 14px;
}
.trigger-icon {
font-size: 18px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.trigger-text {
font-size: 12.5px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
line-height: 1.45;
}
.trigger-text strong {
color: #ff8fa0;
font-weight: 700;
display: block;
font-size: 13px;
}

/* Fixes */
.fixes {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 9px;
margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.fix-card {
background: rgba(100,255,180,0.05);
border: 1px solid rgba(100,255,180,0.15);
border-radius: 13px;
padding: 14px 14px;
position: relative;
}
.fix-card .fix-num {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: 28px;
font-weight: 900;
color: rgba(100,255,180,0.12);
position: absolute;
top: 8px; right: 12px;
line-height: 1;
}
.fix-card .fix-emoji {
font-size: 16px;
margin-bottom: 6px;
display: block;
}
.fix-card .fix-title {
font-size: 12.5px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #7effc5;
margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.fix-card .fix-desc {
font-size: 11px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
line-height: 1.4;
}

/* Bottom bar */
.bottom-bar {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: space-between;
padding-top: 20px;
border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.tldr {
font-size: 12px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
}
.tldr span {
color: #a084ff;
font-weight: 700;
}
.motto {
font-family: ‘Syne’, sans-serif;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 800;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
letter-spacing: 0.05em;
text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Floating ghost */
.ghost-float {
position: absolute;
top: 32px; right: 32px;
font-size: 52px;
opacity: 0.07;
animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
pointer-events: none;
}
@keyframes float {
0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="blob1"></div>
  <div class="blob2"></div>
  <div class="ghost-float">👻</div>

  <div class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>TikTok Survival Guide</div>

  <h1 class="title">
    <span class="ghost">SHADOW</span><br>
    <span class="highlight">BAN</span> 101
  </h1>
  <p class="subtitle">why your views suddenly dropped to 12 💀</p>

  <div class="what-box">
    <div class="label">what it actually is</div>
    <p>TikTok's algo quietly <span>stops pushing your content</span> on the FYP when it thinks you're posting the same thing on repeat. not a real ban — just the algorithm going <span>"ok this again…"</span> and moving on.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">🚨 what triggers it</div>
  <div class="triggers">
    <div class="trigger-row">
      <span class="trigger-icon">♻️</span>
      <div class="trigger-text">
        <strong>Same structure every time</strong>
        same hook format, same slide order, same pacing = reused content signal
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="trigger-row">
      <span class="trigger-icon">📋</span>
      <div class="trigger-text">
        <strong>Copy-paste text overlays</strong>
        swapping pics but keeping the same words? algo still clocks it
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="trigger-row">
      <span class="trigger-icon">🤖</span>
      <div class="trigger-text">
        <strong>Low originality score</strong>
        5 videos that look like 1 video = "spammy behavior" flag
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">✅ how to stay safe</div>
  <div class="fixes">
    <div class="fix-card">
      <span class="fix-num">01</span>
      <span class="fix-emoji">🪝</span>
      <div class="fix-title">Switch the hook</div>
      <div class="fix-desc">new angle, new opening line every time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fix-card">
      <span class="fix-num">02</span>
      <span class="fix-emoji">🔀</span>
      <div class="fix-title">Reorder slides</div>
      <div class="fix-desc">mix up the structure so the flow feels fresh</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fix-card">
      <span class="fix-num">03</span>
      <span class="fix-emoji">✍️</span>
      <div class="fix-title">Rewrite the text</div>
      <div class="fix-desc">same idea, different words — always</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fix-card">
      <span class="fix-num">04</span>
      <span class="fix-emoji">🎯</span>
      <div class="fix-title">New angle</div>
      <div class="fix-desc">add a twist, a plot, a different pov</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-bar">
    <div class="tldr"><span>TL;DR</span> — keep it fresh or stay invisible</div>
    <div class="motto">no originality = no FYP</div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
